Source: distiller-platform-update
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Maintainer: PamirAI Incorporated <founders@pamir.ai>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.7.0
Homepage: https://github.com/pamir-ai-pkgs/distiller-platform-update
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/pamir-ai-pkgs/distiller-platform-update.git
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/pamir-ai-pkgs/distiller-platform-update
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: distiller-platform-update
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         apt,
         systemd,
         udev,
         polkitd | policykit-1,
         lsb-release,
         curl,
         libblockdev-mdraid2,
         distiller-genesis-common | distiller-genesis-cm5 | distiller-genesis-rockchip,
Recommends: ripgrep
Description: Platform update tool for Distiller systems
 Automatically applies platform-level system configuration updates to bring
 older Distiller images up to parity with latest pi-gen builds.
 .
 Updates are applied automatically during package installation/upgrade:
  * APT repository configuration (debian.griffo.io, apt.pamir.ai)
  * System hardware configuration (udev rules)
  * Boot partition optimizations (CPU, fan, SPI, camera)
  * SD card automount support (PolicyKit + udisks2)
  * User and group permissions
  * Environment variables
  * NVM + Node.js v20.19.5 installation for distiller user
  * Claude Code CLI installation (Anthropic AI development assistant)
 .
